title: AFC & NFC South Preview
itunes:title: AFC & NFC South Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are counting down the days until kickoff by previewing each division and this week, the guys talk all things AFC & NFC South (18:52). DJ and Bucky also review the biggest news from the weekend including Odell Beckham's new max deal and Marqise Lee's unfortunate season-ending injury (00:53). The MTS team also gives you the veterans that will bounce back to life this season (7:14) and rookies that stood out during preseason week 3 (10:53).
